{"kanda":6,"sarga":99,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"महोदरेतुनिहतेमहापार्श्वोमहाबलः ।सुग्रीवेणसमीक्ष्याथक्रोधात्सम्ररक्तलोचनः अङ्गदस्यचमूंभीमांक्षोभयामाससायकैः ।","trans":"Gazing at Mahodara killed by Sugriva, mighty Mahaparsva's eyes turned red in anger. He created a commotion in the army of Angada.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवेण","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"महोदरे","m":"Mahodara"},{"d":"निहते","m":"killed"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"महापार्श्वः","m":"Mahparsva"},{"d":"समीक्ष्य","m":"gazing"},{"d":"अथ","m":"then"},{"d":"क्रोधसम्रक्तलोचनः","m":"eyes turned red in anger"},{"d":"सायकैः","m":"army"},{"d":"अङ्गदस्य","m":"in Angada's"},{"d":"भीमाम्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"चमूम्","m":"troops"},{"d":"क्षोभयामास","m":"commotion"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सवानराणांमुख्यानामुत्तमाङ्गानिसर्वशः पातयामानकायेभ्यःफलंवृन्तादिवानिलः ।","trans":"That leader (Mahaparsva) severed the heads of Vanara leaders from their body just as wind drops fruits from stalks.","words":[{"d":"सःसर्वशः","m":"severed"},{"d":"मुख्यानाम्","m":"leader"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"उत्तमाङ्गानि","m":"limbs"},{"d":"वृन्तात्","m":"stalks"},{"d":"फलमिव","m":"fruits like"},{"d":"कायेभ्यः","m":"from body"},{"d":"पातयामास","m":"thrown"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"केषांचिदिषुभिर्बाहुन् स्कन्धांश्छिच्छेदराक्षसः च वानराणांसुङ्कृद्ध: पार्श्वंकेषांव्यदारयत् ।","trans":"Then with his arrows, that Rakshasa (Mahaparsva) shattered the arms of some, shoulders of some, sides, and ribs of some Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"सःराक्षसः","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"सुसङ्कृद्ध:","m":"infuriated"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"बाहून्","m":"arms"},{"d":"स्कन्दाम्","m":"shoulders"},{"d":"इषुभिः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"चिच्छेद","m":"shattered"},{"d":"केषांचित्","m":"some intent upon"},{"d":"पार्श्वम्","m":"sides"},{"d":"व्यदारयत्","m":"tore off"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"तेऽर्दिताबाणवर्षेणमहापार्श्वेनवानराः विषादविमुखाःसर्वेबभूवुर्गतचेतसः ।","trans":"By the rain of arrows of Mahaparsva, the Vanaras were dejected and wore a sad look on their face and lost senses.","words":[{"d":"महापार्श्वेन","m":"Mahaparsva"},{"d":"बाणवर्षेण","m":"rain of arrows"},{"d":"अर्दिताः","m":"dejected"},{"d":"तेवानराः","m":"those Vanaras"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"गतचेतसः","m":"lost senses"},{"d":"बभूवुः","m":"wore"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"निरीक्ष्यबलमुद्विग्नमङ्गदोराक्षसार्दितम् वेगंचक्रेमहावेगमहाबाहुस्समुद्रइवपर्वणि ।","trans":"Observing the army oppressed by the Rakshasa leader, Angada, endowed with broad shoulders, exhibited his might speedily like the ocean on full moon days.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसार्दितम्","m":"oppressed by the Rakshasa leader"},{"d":"उद्विग्नम्","m":"frightened"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"निरीक्ष्य","m":"observing"},{"d":"पर्वणि","m":"full moon days"},{"d":"समुद्रःइव","m":"like an ocean"},{"d":"वेगम्","m":"speedily"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"exhibited"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"आयसंपरिघंगृह्यसूर्यरमशिसमप्रभम् समरेवानरश्रेष्ठोमहापार्श्वेन्यपातयत् ।","trans":"The foremost of the Vanaras (Angada), taking an iron bar flung on Mahaparsva in the battlefield.","words":[{"d":"वानरश्रेष्ठः","m":"foremost of the Vanaras"},{"d":"सूर्यरमशिसमप्रभम्","m":"radiance of sun's rays"},{"d":"आयसम्","m":"shone"},{"d":"परिघम्","m":"iron bar"},{"d":"गृह्य","m":"taking"},{"d":"समरे","m":"to battlefield"},{"d":"महापार्श्वे","m":"Mahaparsva"},{"d":"न्यपातयत्","m":"flung on"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"स तुतेनप्रहारेणमहापार्श्वोविचेतनः ससूतस्स्यन्दनात्तस्माद्विसंज्ञश्चापतद्भुवि ।","trans":"By that hit, Mahaparsva became unconscious and fell on the ground, senseless, from the chariot along with the charioteer.","words":[{"d":"सःमहापार्श्वः","m":"that Mahaparsva"},{"d":"तेनप्रहारेण","m":"by that hit"},{"d":"विचेतनः","m":"lost consciousness"},{"d":"ससूतः","m":"with charioteer"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"from there"},{"d":"स्यन्दनात्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"विसंज्ञः","m":"senseless"},{"d":"भुवि","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"अपतत्","m":"fell"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"स ऋक्षराजस्तेजस्वीनीलाञ्जनचयोपमः निष्पत्यसुमहावीर्यस्स्वाद्व्यूहन्मेघसन्निभात् ।प्रगृह्यगिरिशृङ्गाभांक्रुद्धस्सविपुलांशिलाम् अश्वाञ्जघानतरसाबभञ्जतम् स्यन्दनं च तम् ।","trans":"Jambavantha, the mighty king of Bears, rushed from his army that looked like a dark cloud. The great hero with his army resembling a heap of black mountain, in his fury seized a huge rock resembling a mountain peak, crushed the chariot and struck the horses.","words":[{"d":"तेजस्वी","m":"mighty"},{"d":"नीलाञ्जनचयोपमः","m":"heap of dark black mountain"},{"d":"सुमहावीर्यः","m":"great hero"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"मेघसन्निभात्","m":"like a cloud"},{"d":"स्वयूथात्","m":"their army"},{"d":"निष्पत्य","m":"went"},{"d":"गिरिशृङ्गाभाम्","m":"resembling mountain peak"},{"d":"विपुलाम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"शिलाम्","m":"rock"},{"d":"प्रगृह्य","m":"seizing"},{"d":"तरसा","m":"rushed"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"अश्वान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"स्यन्दनं च","m":"chariot"},{"d":"बभञ्ज","m":"crushed"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"स ऋक्षराजस्तेजस्वीनीलाञ्जनचयोपमः निष्पत्यसुमहावीर्यस्स्वाद्व्यूहन्मेघसन्निभात् ।प्रगृह्यगिरिशृङ्गाभांक्रुद्धस्सविपुलांशिलाम् अश्वाञ्जघानतरसाबभञ्जतम् स्यन्दनं च तम् ।","trans":"Jambavantha, the mighty king of Bears, rushed from his army that looked like a dark cloud. The great hero with his army resembling a heap of black mountain, in his fury seized a huge rock resembling a mountain peak, crushed the chariot and struck the horses.","words":[{"d":"तेजस्वी","m":"mighty"},{"d":"नीलाञ्जनचयोपमः","m":"heap of dark black mountain"},{"d":"सुमहावीर्यः","m":"great hero"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"मेघसन्निभात्","m":"like a cloud"},{"d":"स्वयूथात्","m":"their army"},{"d":"निष्पत्य","m":"went"},{"d":"गिरिशृङ्गाभाम्","m":"resembling mountain peak"},{"d":"विपुलाम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"शिलाम्","m":"rock"},{"d":"प्रगृह्य","m":"seizing"},{"d":"तरसा","m":"rushed"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"अश्वान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"स्यन्दनं च","m":"chariot"},{"d":"बभञ्ज","m":"crushed"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"मु