":"forehead"},{"d":"चाप्यपातयत्","m":"thrown"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"तंसमासाद्यवेगेनवालिपुत्रःप्रतापवान् तलेनाभ्यहनत्क्रुद्धः कर्णमूले सकुण्डले ।","trans":"Courageous son of Vali, enraged, with all speed, slapped the Rakshasa's ear adorned with shining earrings, with his palm.","words":[{"d":"प्रतापवान्स","m":"courageous"},{"d":"वालिपुत्रः","m":"son of Vali"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"enraged"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"speedily"},{"d":"समासाद्य","m":"shining"},{"d":"सकुण्डले","m":"with ear rings"},{"d":"कर्णमूले","m":"decorated"},{"d":"तलेन","m":"with palm"},{"d":"अभ्यहनत्","m":"slapped"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"स तुक्रुद्धोमहावेगोमहापार्श्वोमहाद्युति करेणैकेनजग्राहसुमहान्तंपरश्वथम् ।","trans":"Angry Mahaparsva, who was endowed with speed and shining brightly, took hold of an extraordinary battle axe in one hand.","words":[{"d":"महावेगः","m":"endowed with great speed"},{"d":"महाद्युतिः","m":"shining brightly"},{"d":"सःमहापार्श्वः","m":"that Mahaparsva"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"एकेन","m":"one"},{"d":"करेण","m":"axe"},{"d":"सुमहान्तम्","m":"extraordinary"},{"d":"परश्वथम्","m":"a battle axe"},{"d":"जग्राह","m":"took hold of"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तंम्तैलधौतंविमलंशैलसारमयंदृढम् राक्षसःपरमक्रुद्धोवालिपुत्रेन्यपातयत् ।","trans":"Extremely enraged Rakshasa, hurled at Vali's son that axe that was cleansed with oil, the clean strong axe that was like feet of a mountain.","words":[{"d":"परमक्रुद्धः","m":"extremely enraged"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"तैलधौतम्","m":"smeared with oil"},{"d":"विमलम्","m":"clean"},{"d":"शैलसारमयम्","m":"like feet of mountain"},{"d":"दृढम्","m":"strong"},{"d":"तंम्","m":"that"},{"d":"वालिपुत्रे","m":"Vali's son"},{"d":"न्यपातयत्","m":"hurled"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"तेनवामांसफलकेभृशंप्रत्यवपादितम् अङ्गदोमोक्ष्यामाससरोषस्सपरश्वधम् ।","trans":"Angada, full of fury, escaped Mahaparsva's aim to strike his left shoulder blade in violence.","words":[{"d":"रोषः","m":"full of fury"},{"d":"सःअङ्गदः","m":"that Angada"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by that"},{"d":"वामांसफलके","m":"left shoulder bone"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"in violence"},{"d":"प्रत्यवपादितम्","m":"hurled in turn"},{"d":"परश्वधम्","m":"Parasva's"},{"d":"मोक्ष्यामास","m":"escaped"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"सवीरोवज्रसङ्काशमङ्गदोमुष्टिमात्मनः संवर्तयत्सुसङ्कृद्धःपितृतुल्यपराक्रमः ।","trans":"Angada, who was equal to his father in his prowess, was highly furious and himself clenched his fist which resembled thunderbolt.","words":[{"d":"सुसङ्कृद्धः","m":"highly furious"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"himself"},{"d":"वज्रसङ्काशम्","m":"resembling thunderbolt"},{"d":"मुष्टिम्","m":"fist"},{"d":"सम्वर्तयामास","m":"clenched"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"राक्षसस्यस्तनाभ्याशेमर्मज्ञोहृदयंप्रति इन्द्राशनिमस्पर्शं स मुष्टिंविन्यपातयत् ।","trans":"Angada who knew the vital parts, pierced into the middle of the breasts of the Rakshasa into the heart by his fist which was equal to Indra's thunderbolt.","words":[{"d":"मर्मज्ञः","m":"vital"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"राक्षसस्य","m":"Rakshasa's"},{"d":"स्तनाभ्याशे","m":"middle of the breasts"},{"d":"हृदयंप्रति","m":"into the heart"},{"d":"इन्द्राशनिसमस्पर्शम्","m":"equal to Indra's thunderbolt"},{"d":"मुष्टिम्","m":"fist"},{"d":"विन्यपातयत्","m":"pierced"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"तेनतस्यनिपातेनराक्षसस्यमहामृधे पफालहृदयंचास्य स पपातहतोभुवि ।","trans":"In that great conflict, struck by the fist, the Rakshasa (Mahaparsva's) heart broke and killed and fell on the ground.","words":[{"d":"महामृधे","m":"in that great conflict"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by that"},{"d":"निपातेन","m":"struck by the fist"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"राक्षसस्य","m":"Rakshasa's"},{"d":"हृदयम्","m":"heart"},{"d":"पफाल","m":"broke"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"हतः","m":"was killed"},{"d":"भुवि","m":"ground"},{"d":"पपात","m":"fell"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"स्मिन्निपतितेभूमौतत्सैन्यंसम्प्रचुक्षुभे अभवच्चमहान्क्रोधस्समरेरावणस्यतु ।","trans":"Mahaparsva having fallen down in the battle, the army was bewildered, and Ravana was overcome with anger.","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"his"},{"d":"भूमौ","